Description:

Gods Robots is a dynamic blend of world class songwriting, energetic stage performance, cutting 
edge technology and old school musicianship. The duo's stage show unites original songs with 
Taamara delivering a powerful combination of english lyrics with nuanced classical India stylings 
alongside Janaka Selekta's hard hitting riddims dubbed from his multi-channel electronics platform. Improvisation is a key element of Gods Robots as they move seamlessly from their original songs to a DJ dance format and back again. High energy and LIVE.
